18 DULWICH VILLAGE
JANICE AND MICHAEL RICH
LIVED HAPPILY IN THIS HOUSE FOR 45 YEARS FROM 1966
AND BROUGHT UP THEIR FOUR CHILDREN HERE
IN 1999 THEY PLACED THIS SEAT IN THEIR GARDEN FOR PUBLIC USE
JANICE RICH DIED HERE ON 19th MARCH 2011"Û
